Statusbar Plugin for OpenCPN
=======================================

The status bar plugin provides customizable, easier to read,
and much less cpu usage under linux with gtk than the builtin statusbar.

Compiling
=========
You have to be able to compile OpenCPN itself - Get the info at http://opencpn.org/ocpn/developers_manual

* go to the plugin subdirectory in your OpenCPN source tree
* git clone git://github.com/seandepagnier/statusbar_pi.git

Build as normally:

* cd ..
* cd build
* cmake ..
* cmake --build .

